	(10, 4, 4, NULL, 'Bổ sung thêm về **Hardware Optimization**:\n\n- **RAM**: 32GB là sweet spot, 64GB chỉ cần thiết cho assemblies > 5000 parts\n- **Storage**: NVMe SSD cho OS + SolidWorks, SATA SSD cho project files\n- **Graphics**: Quadro RTX 4000 trở lên cho professional work\n\nĐặc biệt chú ý **Page File** settings - nên set manual 1.5x RAM size.', 0, 0, 0, NULL, 20, 0, 15, 3, 4.31, 4.21, 'unverified', NULL, NULL, '"[\\"hardware\\",\\"performance\\",\\"system\\"]"', 'reference', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-18 10:57:51', '2025-06-22 10:57:51', NULL),
