	(68, 21, 2, NULL, 'Excellent tips! Về **Mesh Quality**, mình thường check:\n\n1. **Aspect Ratio** < 3:1 cho structural analysis\n2. **Skewness** < 0.7 (tốt nhất < 0.5)\n3. **Jacobian** > 0.6\n\nVới ANSYS Mechanical, **Patch Conforming Method** cho geometry phức tạp, **Patch Independent** cho simple parts.', 0, 0, 0, NULL, 19, 0, 1, 0, 4.46, 4.23, 'pending', NULL, NULL, '"[\\"fea\\",\\"meshing\\",\\"ansys\\"]"', 'tutorial', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-23 10:57:51', '2025-06-24 10:57:51', NULL),
