	(107, 35, 24, NULL, 'Về **Tool Selection**, có thể tham khảo bảng này:\n\n**Aluminum 6061:**\n- Roughing: Uncoated carbide, 3 flutes\n- Finishing: Polished carbide, 2 flutes\n- Coating: Tránh TiN (dễ stick)\n\n**Steel 1045:**\n- Roughing: TiAlN coated, 4 flutes\n- Finishing: TiN coated, 2-3 flutes\n- Coolant: Bắt buộc phải có\n\nChipload formula: **Feed = RPM × Flutes × Chipload**', 0, 0, 1, 'Feed = RPM \\times Flutes \\times Chipload', 17, 4, 13, 1, 3.85, 3.65, 'unverified', NULL, NULL, '"[\\"tooling\\",\\"feeds-speeds\\",\\"materials\\"]"', 'reference', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-18 10:57:52', '2025-06-22 10:57:52', NULL),
